data.description: Open-house this Saturday, 2/3/2024 from 2pm - 4pm, light refreshments will be served.       Ideally located within the highly sought-after Kentmorr AirPark subdivision and nestled within the esteemed Matapeake school district, this property is a true gem. This three-level, chalet style home boats five bedrooms, three bathrooms and a uniquely design basement.  A modern kitchen with stainless steel appliances and granite countertops, solar panels through out, a storage shed, and  new water filtration system and washer and dryer installed in 2023. Please note this home is scheduled to connect to the Kent Island sewage system in about 30 days. Adding to its appeal this home is conveniently situated in walking distance to the iconic Kentmorr Restaurant (where you can arrive by land, air or sea), a private beach, marina and elks lodge. Sellers will have home professionally cleaned upon sale. Don’t miss your chance to embrace the coastal lifestyle and indulge in the finest amenities this enchanting area has to offer.
